name: Validate CRUD functionality related to Articles

elements.name: As a logged in user, I should be able to create an article

steps.name: User clicks on sign in link
User enters 'test1223@gmail.com' and 'test@123'
User signs in
User should be logged in with 'testuserfollow'
User clicks on New Post link
User fills all the article creation details with title 'title create'
User clicks button Publish Article
User validates the published article for user 'testuserfollow'
User clicks on Home link
User clicks on Global feed
User should be able to see article created

elements.name: As a logged in user, I should be able to edit an article

steps.name: User navigates to his profile 'testuserfollow'
User clicks on the first avaiable article
User clicks on 'edit' article in article overview
User updates Article Description
User clicks button Publish Article
User should see the article updated

elements.name: As a logged in user, I should be able to edit an article

steps.name: User navigates to his profile 'testuserfollow'
User clicks on the first avaiable article
User clicks on 'delete' article in article overview
User navigates to his profile 'testuserfollow'
User should not be able to see article deleted
